need_candidates.comment_requirements:
Here are the requirements for the User/IT support:

We are looking for individuals to provide first line user/IT support to our current customer base.  This requires solving simple computer problems.  Issues are reported to our helpdesk software (Jira) and via phone.  The skills needed are the following:
-Good English skills, written and verbal
-Good knowledge of Microsoft Windows.  This includes knowledge of how to:
-Install software
-Elevate user privileges (run as administrator)
-Manage settings and configurations in windows such as changing screen resolution, install printer drivers, change language and regional settings, add shortcuts to desktop, local user management (add user, change password etc.)
-Some networking knowledge would be beneficial
-Understand IP address basics (what an IP address is, how it is used)
-Knowledge of simple tools such as ping
-Understanding statistics from speedtest.net (latency, upload speed, download speed)
-No criminal record

We need someone who is ready for a long-term commitment.  We intend on investing considerable time and effort in training and preparing this individual for the job.  We require someone who is ready to stay on board for at least 3-5 years.  The job may require traveling to Iceland for training and preparation.  Travel and accommodation costs will be covered by us.

name: Samir Shnino
note:
Update
Hello Volodymyr!

I am sorry for the very late answer. We've been working on our projects and were very busy.

We work with Smart City Solutions but have always been asked to develop mobile and web applications for other companies and the public sector. We don't have the capacity for that, but we are looking for a collaboration with a Ukrainian company to look like a part of our company.

Many Ukrainian companies have connected us and have different suggestions for how we can collaborate. Swedish companies and the public sector find it much easier to deal with Swedish companies than other companies from other countries. So we will stand for project leading, selling, and marketing, and the company we want to collaborate with will be responsible for designing, developing and quality assurance. If this is something interesting for you, we can have a meeting and discuss a possible win-win business model.

BR 
Samir

We would like you to prepare what clients you have now, what projects you developed and are online that we look at, How many you developers you have in your team, what competences you have and maybe prepare two collaboration proposals. 

BR
Samir

need_candidates.comment_requirements: Samir is interested in front end developer for mobile applications, React Native. Also he needs part time web designer and UX/UI, back end and Java developer SMM, but all depends on certain project. This project will start in 2- 3 month
